{
  "total_duration": 463.145,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 15.28,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果班里做海报、搭 LEGO、布置教室，最大的一组一定赢吗？不一定。有的作品东西最多，有的同学最努力，但最后获胜的，可能是最整洁、最清楚、最有趣的设计。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 15.63,
      "end": 26.07,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的故事表面上是花园比赛，其实是在玩一个比较游戏：比大小、比努力、比数量、比设计，结果可能完全不同。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 26.42,
      "end": 38.944,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "题目"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The best and the worst"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，最好的和最差的，会先让你以为这是夸奖最漂亮的花园，最后却突然变成一个很可爱的自嘲笑话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 39.293,
      "end": 54.485,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事一开始："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Joe Sanders has the most beautiful garden in our town."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "乔·桑德斯有镇上最漂亮的花园。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the most beautiful"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示在所有花园里，它最突出，是“最美的”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 54.835,
      "end": 73.347,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "每年，几乎每个人都会参加"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Nicest Garden Competition"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，最佳花园竞赛。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "enters for"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是“走进”，而是“报名参加、加入一个比赛”。乔每次都赢："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Joe wins every time."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 73.696,
      "end": 95.2,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是比尔·弗里斯看起来也很厉害。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Bill Frith's garden is larger than Joe's."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他的花园更大；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Bill works harder than Joe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他比乔更努力；他还种了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "more flowers and vegetables"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，更多花和蔬菜。按大小、努力、数量来比，比尔都很强。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 95.55,
      "end": 132.149,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但故事翻到另一个标准：乔的花园"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "is more interesting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，更有趣。他有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neat paths"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，整洁的小路；有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a wooden bridge"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，木桥；还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a pool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是游泳池，而是花园里的小池塘或水景。最后叙述者也参加比赛，却总是赢一个小奖："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "for the worst garden"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，因为他的花园是镇上最差的。这不是骂人，而是在笑自己喜欢花园、却不喜欢辛苦劳动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 132.499,
      "end": 137.539,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课最重要的问题不是“谁会种花”，而是“你按什么标准来比较”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 137.889,
      "end": 142.972,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就像一个小组作品，可能有的最大，有的最整齐，有的最有趣？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 143.322,
      "end": 159.001,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。课文里比尔的花园"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "larger than Joe's"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，更大；他"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "works harder than Joe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，更努力；他种了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "more flowers and vegetables"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，数量更多。这些都是很清楚的标准。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 159.351,
      "end": 161.981,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那为什么乔还能赢？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 162.331,
      "end": 182.011,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为乔赢的是整体效果。他的花园"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "more interesting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，更有设计感。整洁的小路让人知道往哪里走，木桥和小池塘让花园有一个可以看的重点。就像海报不一定贴满最多图片才最好，清楚、有顺序、有亮点也很重要。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 182.36,
      "end": 187.798,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "best"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是永远等于"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "biggest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 188.147,
      "end": 208.827,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "完全正确。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "best"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“按这次评比标准，整体最好”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "biggest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "只是在大小上最大。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "harder"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是努力更多。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "more"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是数量更多。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "more interesting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是设计和感觉更吸引人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 209.176,
      "end": 213.899,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那最后叙述者得最差花园的小奖，是不是很丢脸？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 214.249,
      "end": 236.305,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的幽默是自嘲，不是嘲笑别人。他说自己也喜欢花园，但"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I do not like hard work"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，我不喜欢辛苦劳动。所以他每年也参加比赛，还总能赢一个小奖，只不过是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the worst garden"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。读到这里，你会发现他也是“常胜选手”，只是赢的方向和乔相反。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 236.655,
      "end": 243.097,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "原来同一个比赛里，可以有最美、最大、最努力、最多、最有趣，也可以有最差。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 243.447,
      "end": 255.846,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，这就是今天的比较网络。比较之前，先问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "compare what?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比什么？大小、努力、数量、设计、美感，还是最后的笑点？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 256.196,
      "end": 260.108,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Joe Sanders has the most beautiful garden in our town."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 260.458,
      "end": 266.458,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Nearly everybody enters for 'The Nicest Garden Competition' each year, but Joe wins every time."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 266.808,
      "end": 269.928,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Bill Frith's garden is larger than Joe's."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 270.278,
      "end": 276.206,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Bill works harder than Joe and grows more flowers and vegetables, but Joe's garden is more interesting."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 276.556,
      "end": 280.756,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He has made neat paths and has built a wooden bridge over a pool."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 281.106,
      "end": 284.754,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I like gardens too, but I do not like hard work."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 285.104,
      "end": 291.968,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Every year I enter for the garden competition too, and I always win a little prize for the worst garden in the town!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 292.317,
      "end": 295.221,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "competition"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "competition"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 295.571,
      "end": 297.395,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "competition"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "competition"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 297.745,
      "end": 315.025,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "competition"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "competition"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“比赛、竞赛、评比”。它不只可以是运动比赛，也可以是海报评比、手工作品比赛、教室布置比赛。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "garden competition"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是大家拿自己的花园来参加评比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 315.375,
      "end": 317.959,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "neat"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 318.308,
      "end": 319.748,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "neat"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 320.098,
      "end": 336.914,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "neat"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neat"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是“整洁的、有条理的”。它不是说东西很多，而是说摆放清楚、看起来舒服。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neat paths"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，就是整洁的小路，让花园看起来有秩序、有设计。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 337.264,
      "end": 340.016,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "path"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "path"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 340.366,
      "end": 341.878,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "path"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "path"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 342.228,
      "end": 359.931,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "path"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "path"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“小路、路径”。在花园里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "paths"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "会告诉人怎么走，也会把不同区域分开。乔的花园有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "neat paths"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，所以它不只是花多，而是有结构、好参观。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 360.281,
      "end": 400.388,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的语法就是“按不同标准比较”。看一张评委表：大小上，比尔的花园"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "is larger than Joe's"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；努力上，比尔"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "works harder than Joe"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；数量上，比尔"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grows more flowers and vegetables"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；设计感上，乔的花园"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "is more interesting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；整体美感上，乔有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the most beautiful garden"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；最后笑点上，叙述者赢了"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the worst garden"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。所以比较句不是只背"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "-er"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "more"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，更要先问：我在比较哪一个维度？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 400.738,
      "end": 417.978,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天这个“比较标准”放进你自己的现代场景。下面三个空都要填：海报评比、积木作品、整洁桌面。你从 word bank 里选短语，重点是说清楚：更大、更努力、更多，不一定等于最后最好。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 418.328,
      "end": 430.395,
      "speaker": "A",
